OL,3,CThousands more shoplifting offences
OL,4,Crecorded in 'epidemic of retail crime'
OL,6,FShoplifting offences also increased in
OL,7,FDevon and Cornwall (38%),
OL,8,FGloucestershire (33%) and Dorset (19%).
OL,10,FAcross England and Wales, the number
OL,11,Fof shoplifting offences recorded by
OL,12,Fpolice rose by 29% to reach a 20-year
OL,13,Fhigh.
OL,15,FUdsaw, the retail trade union, said
OL,16,Fshoplifting is becoming "increasingly
OL,17,Fcommon" and it is "hugely concerned".
